		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸角鳄的角左右晃动，发射2个水刃，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，最后使用尾部发射水刃，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玩家处在其后方时，圣骸角鳄转身甩尾造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，圣骸角鳄张着嘴冲过来，造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="991" width="425" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸角鳄从开局、瘫痪恢复后或者吸收<span color="#00a4f9">「噬骸能量块·水」</span><span>之后，将进行抗性强化：</span><span color="#99e6ff">水抗+60%，其他抗性+30%</span><span>，并且全身变亮；该效果持续到其施放</span><span color="#00a4f9">「鲸戏水」</span><span>技能后，或被携带有</span><span color="#00a4f9">「噬骸能量块·水」</span><span>的玩家命中后失效。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸角鳄.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1394" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸角鳄.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1390" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸角鳄.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸角鳄.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1390" y="906">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸角鳄.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸角鳄进行右划、冲咬、甩尾、翻砸四段攻击，分别造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,70%,80%,<br/>100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸角鳄进行上咬合攻击，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害，顺势倒下翻滚，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，圣骸角鳄如龙蜥般潜入地面，期间触碰持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">10%</span><span>伤害，至玩家处钻出，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害，并顺势落地，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="440" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每45s-60s，圣骸角鳄在玩家处生成大水喷，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害，接着在外环进行二次水喷，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，形成</span><span color="#00a4f8">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#00a4f8">噬骸能量块·水</span><span color="#00a4f8">」</span><span>；此时角鳄失去强化，6s后则会被角鳄吸收恢复强化。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
